topic.title: Configuration Space Registers

body.p: Switchtec uses a Type 1 Configuration Header for the upstream and downstream P2P bridges as illustrated. Unless noted otherwise, all the fields in the PCIe Configuration Space are compliant to the PCIe specification.

table.title: PCIe Type 1 Header - P2P Configuration Space
